title: NETWORK_GET_ENTITY_FROM_NETWORK_ID
content:
0xCE4E5D9B0A4FF5600x5B912C3F// NetworkGetEntityFromNetworkId
Entity NETWORK_GET_ENTITY_FROM_NETWORK_ID(int netId);Parameters:netId: the network id of the entityReturns: The local entity handle of the network idGet the local entity handle of the given network idThrough this native you can get back the entity that you previously converted to netid with NetworkGetNetworkIdFromEntity or with the ToNet nativesExamples:LuaJavaScriptC#local entity = NetworkGetEntityFromNetworkId(netId)
